# César Gómez Portfolio — core conventions

## Project structure

| Path | Purpose |
| ---- | ------- |
| `app/components/` | Section components (`HeroSection`, `AboutSection`, etc.) |
| `app/composables/` | Shared composables (`useTheme`, `useMotionConfig`) |
| `app/assets/css/` | Global styles (`main.css`, Tailwind 4) |
| `i18n/locales/` | en.json, es.json — canonical i18n (not `app/locales/`) |
| `public/img/` | Static images, avatars, logo |
| `scripts/` | Avatar fetch/scrape utilities |

## Stack

Nuxt 4 · Vue 3 `<script setup>` · TypeScript · PrimeVue · Tailwind 4 · motion-v · @nuxtjs/i18n · Netlify (`cesargomez.dev`)

## Dev vs production URLs

- **Dev:** `http://localhost:3000/`
- **Prod:** `https://cesargomez.dev` (Netlify)
- **Legacy redirect:** `https://mrcego.github.io/me` → `https://cesargomez.dev`

## TypeScript & Vue

- Composition API with `<script setup lang="ts">`
- `defineProps` / `defineEmits` with types; avoid `any`
- motion-v: use `:while-in-view`, not `:in-view`
- PrimeVue Dialog teleported to body — modal styles belong in `main.css`, not transparent `glass`

## i18n

- All user-facing strings via `$t()` / `useI18n()`
- Role modal content under `about.roles.{key}.*`
- Edit `i18n/locales/en.json` and `es.json` together

## Commands

`pnpm dev` · `pnpm lint` · `pnpm typecheck` · `pnpm generate` · `pnpm prepush:validate`

## Fix as you go

In files you touch: keep scope minimal, match existing patterns, run lint/typecheck before push.
